{"name":"Destiné","permission":{"default":0,"Yuxcl9CkCsyz68AJ":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>Il semble que vous soyez destin&eacute; &agrave; accomplir de grandes choses. Vous poss&eacute;dez un nombre maximal de points de destin &eacute;gal &agrave; votre bonus de ma&icirc;trise. Vous r&eacute;cup&eacute;rez 1 point de destin apr&egrave;s chaque repos long.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Vous pouvez d&eacute;penser un point de destin pour obtenir 10 au r&eacute;sultat d'un d20, m&ecirc;me apr&egrave;s avoir pris connaissance du r&eacute;sultat, mais avant de d&eacute;terminer l'issue de l'action.</li>\n<li>Vous pouvez d&eacute;penser 3 points de destin pour obtenir un bonus de +10 sur le r&eacute;sultat d'un test de caract&eacute;ristique ou d'un <a href=\"https://5e-drs.fr/combattre#jets-dattaque\">jet d'attaque</a> ou <a href=\"https://5e-drs.fr/utiliser-les-caracteristiques#jets-de-sauvegarde\">de sauvegarde</a>.</li>\n</ul>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"featType":{"value":"","_deprecated":true},"requirements":"","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"time":{"value":"","_deprecated":true},"damageType":{"value":"","_deprecated":true}},"flags":{},"img":"modules/compendiums-mix-dnd5e/assets/srd-heros-et-dragons/icons/destine.jpg","_id":"abPz9TP8oUwudLnR"}
